transcript:
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Ya hello mam, very good, very good morning. Renu Handicrafts mein baat ho rahi hai?
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Kon? Ji mam, Renu Handicrafts mein baat ho rahi hai, mein Kajal baat kar rahi hu IndiaMART se.
Customer: Ji, ok mein abhi mere dada namaz padh rahe hai baad mein baat karunga.
Executive: Accha, theek hai fir aap mujhe bata do kab tak baat ho jayegi sir se?
Customer: Kis cheez ke bare mein?
Executive: Renu Handicrafts ke bare mein mam. Aur Sikandar ji se baat ho jayegi meri abhi?
Customer: Wo bhi, abhi to dukan gaye hai.
Executive: Dukan gaye hue hai?
Customer: Yes mam.
Executive: Theek hai koi baat nahi, fir mein sir se hi baat kar leti hu ek baar.
Customer: Abhi aayenge jab baat karate hai.
Executive: Kab tak aa jayenge aap bata rahi mujhe?
Customer: Abhi 5 minute mein aa jayenge.
Executive: 5 minute mein aa jayenge?
Customer: Haan.
Executive: Theek hai fir jab aa jaye to aap mujhe call kar lijiyega isi number pe, theek hai?
Customer: Yes mam.
Executive: Okay, thank you.
Customer: Thank you.
summary:
Concerns:

- Executive wants to talk to Mr. Sikandar.

- Customer says he is at the shop.



Resolution:

- Executive will call back later.



Next Steps: 

- Customer will call back in 5 minutes.

None
